        <sect2 xml:id="sec-install-java">
            <title>Installing Java</title>
            <para>Oracle WebLogic Server 12cR2 (12.2.1) requires JDK version 1.8. Log in to the
                target system (&sls; 12 64-bit operating system) as a non-administration user.
                Download the Java SE Development Kit 8 (jdk-8u91-linux- x64.tar.gz) from <link
                    xlink:href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/indexes/downloads/index.html#java"
                />. </para>

            <para>Set the environment variables JAVA_HOME and PATH to ensure the proper JDK version
                is installed and ready for use.</para>

